    "link": "https://energy.ec.europa.eu/news/commission-and-eu-countries-coordinate-and-assess-situation-oil-and-gas-markets-2026-03-13_en",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-13T08:06:31.000Z",
    "content": "<p>In separate ad hoc meetings of the Gas Coordination Group and the Oil Coordination Group held yesterday, the Commission and EU countries coordinated and assessed the situation concerning the EU’s gas and oil security of supply in view of the continued disruptions in the Middle East.</p>",
